-- NBA Commissioner David Stern to Step Down in February 2014
-- B y   M a s o n   L e v i n s o n   a n d   S c o t t   S o s h n i c k
-- 2012-10-25T17:43:22Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-10-25/nba-commissioner-david-stern-to-step-down-in-february-2014.html
David Stern will step down as
commissioner of the National Basketball Association in February
2014, after 30 years on the job.  The league’s board said it would negotiate with Deputy
Commissioner Adam Silver to be Stern’s successor, and have a
contract in place by April 2013.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Larry Siddons at 
 lsiddons@bloomberg.net  